      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride with plenty of personality? This well-maintained vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next chapter! While it shows some honest signs of use and cosmetic wear from its time on the road, it remains a solid, reliable choice for anyone seeking a quality driving experience at a great value. It's a fantastic opportunity to own a capable car that still has many miles left to go!",
