      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, well-maintained condition and serves as a reliable daily driver. The exterior retains a nice shine, though there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. Mechanically, it remains very strong, with a smooth engine and transmission, and all major features are fully functional. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that has been cared for properly and is ready for its next owner.",
