      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle stands as a testament to meticulous preservation and uncompromising maintenance. Every facet of this specimen, from its lustrous finish to its pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care typically reserved for private collections. We invite the most discerning enthusiasts to experience an automotive offering that transcends the ordinary.",
